The paper deals with image enhancement using generative adversarial networks (GANs) and reinforcement learning, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of image editing software, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves image processing and graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with enhancing images and faces.
